      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic opportunity to own a dependable and hard-working vehicle! This car is in fair condition, showing some honest character and wear from its journeys, but it remains a solid and reliable choice for your daily needs. It's the perfect match for someone seeking great value and a car that's ready to hit the road today!",
