    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. While it remains mechanically functional, it shows clear signs of age including several noticeable exterior scratches, minor dents, and some fading paint on the hood. The interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some cracked plastic trim, but all essential electronics and climate controls are operational. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 18500.0,
